The '''Center for Advanced Biotechnology and Medicine''' (CABM) is located on [[Busch Campus (Rutgers University)|Busch Campus]] in [[Piscataway, New Jersey]]. It was established in 1985 to advance knowledge in the [[life sciences]] for the improvement of human health. It is administered by [[Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey]]. The building was completed in 1990, and has {{convert|100000|sqft|m2|-4}} of lab and office space.

